Here is a list of 10 budget-friendly restaurants in West Palm Beach and Atlanta that offer breakfast, lunch, and dinner:

## West Palm Beach:
1. Aggarwal Bikaner Wala - Serving French, BBQ, and fast food with an average cost of $17.
2. Krunchies - Offering desserts, tea, BBQ, Chinese, and American cuisine for an average of $20.
3. Citron - With a variety of options including tea, French, bakery, BBQ, and Indian food, and averaging $18.
4. Kalpak Restaurant & Cafe - Known for its tea, Mexican, and pizza, with an average cost of $24.
5. Cafe' Wow - Specializing in Chinese, BBQ, and desserts, this restaurant has an average price tag of $24.
6. Neha's Treat - A cafe serving pizza, BBQ, and more, with an average cost of $30.
7. Prem Rasoi - Fast food, Chinese, cafe, and seafood options are available here for around $34.
8. Punjab Patiyala Sahi - Focusing on desserts, fast food, cafe, Mediterranean, and seafood, the average cost is $35.
9. Chanakya Bar-Be-Que - This pizza and fast food joint has an average cost of $68.
10. Anand Ji - Serving tea, cafe, BBQ, and fast food, Anand Ji's average cost is $57.

## Atlanta:
1. Barkat - A bakery, Indian, and Mediterranean haven with an average cost of $78.
2. Saffron - With tea, cafe, fast food, and seafood options, Saffron averages $39.
3. Ahata - Tea, Indian, and desserts are on the menu here, with an average cost of $17.
4. Caboose X Cafe & Lounge - Offering bakery, fast food, Chinese, Indian, and seafood dishes for around $23.
5. Chocadoodledoo - Specializing in BBQ, pizza, Indian, and desserts, and averaging $24.
6. Nawaab - Known for its desserts, tea, pizza, French, and cafe, with an average cost of $24.
7. Beliram Degchiwala - A cafe and pizza spot with an average price of $35.
8. The Krib - Seafood, BBQ, and Italian dishes are served here for an average of $45.

10. China Hot - Tea, cafe, and BBQ for an affordable $13.

Please note that the average costs provided are estimates and may vary depending on the specific dishes and portions chosen. It's always a good idea to check the menu and prices directly with the restaurants for the most accurate information.

Certainly! Here is a list of 10 free or low-cost attractions in West Palm Beach and Atlanta, along with some additional information: 

## West Palm Beach:
- There is limited information available about attractions in West Palm Beach. However, it is worth checking out the local beaches, which are a great way to enjoy the outdoors and the beautiful Florida coast for free. 

## Atlanta:
1. **Atlanta Botanical Garden**: A beautiful, tranquil escape in the heart of the city. While there is an admission fee, it is relatively low, and they often have special offers and discounts. 

> Address: 1345 Piedmont Ave NE, Atlanta, GA 30309, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 876-5859
>
> Website: https://www.atlantabg.org/

2. **World of Coca-Cola**: A museum dedicated to the history of Coca-Cola, offering a fun and interactive experience. 

> Address: 121 Baker St NW, Atlanta, GA 30313, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 676-5151
>
> Website: https://www.worldofcoca-cola.com/

3. **Georgia Aquarium**: This aquarium offers an immersive experience with a variety of aquatic life. There is an admission fee, but they often have special ticket offers and discounts. 

> Address: 225 Baker St NW, Atlanta, GA 30313, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 581-4000
>
> Website: https://www.georgiaaquarium.org/

4. **Martin Luther King, Jr. National Historical Park**: A significant historical site dedicated to the life and legacy of Martin Luther King Jr., offering free admission and an important educational experience. 

> Address: 450 Auburn Ave NE, Atlanta, GA 30312, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 331-5190
>
> Website: https://www.nps.gov/malu/index.htm 

5. **Piedmont Park**: A large, urban park offering a peaceful escape with plenty of green space, walking trails, and recreational activities. Entry is free. 

> Address: Atlanta, GA 30309, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 875-7275
>
> Website: https://piedmontpark.org/

6. **High Museum of Art**: A renowned art museum featuring a diverse collection of art, offering a cultural experience. While there is an admission fee, they have various free events and discounted tickets on certain days. 

> Address: 1280 Peachtree St NE, Atlanta, GA 30309, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 733-4400
>
> Website: https://www.high.org/

7. **SkyView Atlanta**: An iconic Ferris wheel offering panoramic views of the city. Entry is free, and you can choose to pay to ride for a fee. 

> Address: 168 Luckie St NW, Atlanta, GA 30303, USA
>
> Phone: (678) 949-9023
>
> Website: http://www.skyviewatlanta.com/

8. **Centennial Olympic Park**: A beautiful park with a rich Olympic history, offering a relaxing green space with various attractions and events. Entry is free. 

> Address: Atlanta, GA 30313, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 223-4412
>
> Website: https://www.gwcca.org/centennial-olympic-park

9. **Zoo Atlanta**: A zoo featuring a range of animals, offering an educational and fun experience. They have various admission options, including discounted tickets for certain days and times. 

> Address: 800 Cherokee Ave SE, Atlanta, GA 30315, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 624-5600
>
> Website: https://zooatlanta.org/

10. **Atlanta History Center**: A cultural and historical museum offering a look into Atlanta's past. While there is an admission fee, they have free days and discounted tickets for certain groups. 

> Address: 130 W Paces Ferry Rd NW, Atlanta, GA 30305, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 814-4000
>
> Website: http://www.atlantahistorycenter.com/ 

These attractions offer a mix of cultural, educational, and recreational experiences, providing plenty of entertainment without breaking the bank.

functions.name: submit_day_plan
functions.desc:
Once you have collected information about the trip, call this function once for each day of the trip, starting on day 1.
If a field does not apply for a given day, use "-" to indicate this.
You MUST call this function to save the plan for each query.

current_city.description: The city for this day. If the plan is to travel between two cities, indicate it as "from A to B" (e.g. "from Ithaca to Charlotte").

transportation.description: e.g. "Flight Number: F3633413, from Ithaca to Charlotte, Departure Time: 05:38, Arrival Time: 07:46"

breakfast.description: The name of a restaurant in the city, e.g. "Nagaland's Kitchen, Charlotte"

attraction.description: Use a ";" to separate different attractions, with each attraction formatted as "Name, City". e.g. "The Charlotte Museum of History, Charlotte;"

accommodation.description: e.g. "Affordable Spacious Refurbished Room in Bushwick!, Charlotte"

chat_history.content:
Here is a list of 10 budget-friendly restaurants in West Palm Beach and Atlanta that offer breakfast, lunch, and dinner:

## West Palm Beach:
1. Aggarwal Bikaner Wala - Serving French, BBQ, and fast food with an average cost of $17.
2. Krunchies - Offering desserts, tea, BBQ, Chinese, and American cuisine for an average of $20.
3. Citron - With a variety of options including tea, French, bakery, BBQ, and Indian food, and averaging $18.
4. Kalpak Restaurant & Cafe - Known for its tea, Mexican, and pizza, with an average cost of $24.
5. Cafe' Wow - Specializing in Chinese, BBQ, and desserts, this restaurant has an average price tag of $24.
6. Neha's Treat - A cafe serving pizza, BBQ, and more, with an average cost of $30.
7. Prem Rasoi - Fast food, Chinese, cafe, and seafood options are available here for around $34.
8. Punjab Patiyala Sahi - Focusing on desserts, fast food, cafe, Mediterranean, and seafood, the average cost is $35.
9. Chanakya Bar-Be-Que - This pizza and fast food joint has an average cost of $68.
10. Anand Ji - Serving tea, cafe, BBQ, and fast food, Anand Ji's average cost is $57.

## Atlanta:
1. Barkat - A bakery, Indian, and Mediterranean haven with an average cost of $78.
2. Saffron - With tea, cafe, fast food, and seafood options, Saffron averages $39.
3. Ahata - Tea, Indian, and desserts are on the menu here, with an average cost of $17.
4. Caboose X Cafe & Lounge - Offering bakery, fast food, Chinese, Indian, and seafood dishes for around $23.
5. Chocadoodledoo - Specializing in BBQ, pizza, Indian, and desserts, and averaging $24.
6. Nawaab - Known for its desserts, tea, pizza, French, and cafe, with an average cost of $24.
7. Beliram Degchiwala - A cafe and pizza spot with an average price of $35.
8. The Krib - Seafood, BBQ, and Italian dishes are served here for an average of $45.
9. Sethi's Restaurant & Barbeque - Pizza, American, bakery, cafe, Indian, and seafood options at an average of $19.
10. China Hot - Tea, cafe, and BBQ for an affordable $13.

Please note that the average costs provided are estimates and may vary depending on the specific dishes and portions chosen. It's always a good idea to check the menu and prices directly with the restaurants for the most accurate information.

Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

Certainly! Here is a list of 10 free or low-cost attractions in West Palm Beach and Atlanta, along with some additional information: 

## West Palm Beach:
- There is limited information available about attractions in West Palm Beach. However, it is worth checking out the local beaches, which are a great way to enjoy the outdoors and the beautiful Florida coast for free. 

## Atlanta:
1. **Atlanta Botanical Garden**: A beautiful, tranquil escape in the heart of the city. While there is an admission fee, it is relatively low, and they often have special offers and discounts. 

> Address: 1345 Piedmont Ave NE, Atlanta, GA 30309, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 876-5859
>
> Website: https://www.atlantabg.org/

2. **World of Coca-Cola**: A museum dedicated to the history of Coca-Cola, offering a fun and interactive experience. 

> Address: 121 Baker St NW, Atlanta, GA 30313, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 676-5151
>
> Website: https://www.worldofcoca-cola.com/

3. **Georgia Aquarium**: This aquarium offers an immersive experience with a variety of aquatic life. There is an admission fee, but they often have special ticket offers and discounts. 

> Address: 225 Baker St NW, Atlanta, GA 30313, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 581-4000
>
> Website: https://www.georgiaaquarium.org/

4. **Martin Luther King, Jr. National Historical Park**: A significant historical site dedicated to the life and legacy of Martin Luther King Jr., offering free admission and an important educational experience. 

> Address: 450 Auburn Ave NE, Atlanta, GA 30312, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 331-5190
>
> Website: https://www.nps.gov/malu/index.htm 

5. **Piedmont Park**: A large, urban park offering a peaceful escape with plenty of green space, walking trails, and recreational activities. Entry is free. 

> Address: Atlanta, GA 30309, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 875-7275
>
> Website: https://piedmontpark.org/

6. **High Museum of Art**: A renowned art museum featuring a diverse collection of art, offering a cultural experience. While there is an admission fee, they have various free events and discounted tickets on certain days. 

> Address: 1280 Peachtree St NE, Atlanta, GA 30309, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 733-4400
>
> Website: https://www.high.org/

7. **SkyView Atlanta**: An iconic Ferris wheel offering panoramic views of the city. Entry is free, and you can choose to pay to ride for a fee. 

> Address: 168 Luckie St NW, Atlanta, GA 30303, USA
>
> Phone: (678) 949-9023
>
> Website: http://www.skyviewatlanta.com/

8. **Centennial Olympic Park**: A beautiful park with a rich Olympic history, offering a relaxing green space with various attractions and events. Entry is free. 

> Address: Atlanta, GA 30313, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 223-4412
>
> Website: https://www.gwcca.org/centennial-olympic-park

9. **Zoo Atlanta**: A zoo featuring a range of animals, offering an educational and fun experience. They have various admission options, including discounted tickets for certain days and times. 

> Address: 800 Cherokee Ave SE, Atlanta, GA 30315, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 624-5600
>
> Website: https://zooatlanta.org/

10. **Atlanta History Center**: A cultural and historical museum offering a look into Atlanta's past. While there is an admission fee, they have free days and discounted tickets for certain groups. 

> Address: 130 W Paces Ferry Rd NW, Atlanta, GA 30305, USA
>
> Phone: (404) 814-4000
>
> Website: http://www.atlantahistorycenter.com/ 

These attractions offer a mix of cultural, educational, and recreational experiences, providing plenty of entertainment without breaking the bank.

functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

functions.name: accommodation_search
functions.desc:
Discover accommodations in your desired city.
Example: accommodation_search("Rome") would present a list of hotel rooms in Rome.

city.description: The name of the city where you're seeking accommodation.

functions.name: attraction_search
functions.desc:
Find attractions in a city of your choice.
Example: attraction_search("London") would return attractions in London.

city.description: The name of the city where you're seeking attractions.

functions.name: city_search
functions.desc:
Find cities in a state of your choice.
Example: city_search("California") would return cities in California.

state.description: The name of the state where you're seeking cities.

functions.name: flight_search
functions.desc:
A flight information retrieval tool.
Example: flight_search("New York", "London", "2022-10-01") would fetch flights from New York to London on October 1, 2022.

departure_city.description: The city you'll be flying out from.

destination_city.description: The city you aim to reach.

date.description: The date of your travel in YYYY-MM-DD format.

functions.name: google_distance_matrix
functions.desc:
Estimate the distance, time and cost between two cities.
Example: google_distance_matrix("Paris", "Lyon", "self-driving") would provide driving distance, time and cost between Paris and Lyon.

origin.description: The departure city of your journey.

destination.description: The destination city of your journey.

functions.name: restaurant_search
functions.desc:
Explore dining options in a city of your choice.
Example: restaurant_search("Tokyo") would show a curated list of restaurants in Tokyo.

city.description: The name of the city where you're seeking restaurants.
